#### Adding to the Wider Engineering Retrospective

Contributing to the wider engineering retrospective can be helpful for other groups and the engineering organization as a whole. To include items in the wider retrospective, we vote on items from our own retrospectives, positive or negative, with some affirmation style emoji like +1, üëç, üíØ on or before the 1st of each month. After voting, the EM will add it to [the agenda](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1nEkM_7Dj4bT21GJy0Ut3By76FZqCfLBmFQNVThmW2TY/edit) for that meeting.

